name: Unleashed Beast
description: Unleashed Beast - The best ever seen token which allows holders to ticevere dividends in WBNB. Unleashed Beast network is the opportunity to receive dividends. As the token's network grows and more transactions occur, a portion of the transaction fees generated is allocated to a dividend pool. These dividends are then distributed proportionally to token holders, providing them with a direct financial incentive for their participation and investment in the ecosystem. This dividend distribution mechanism not only rewards token holders for their continued support but also fosters a sense of community engagement and ownership, aligning the interests of participants with the overall success and growth of the $BEAST token.
